data.title: To my brother Roy on his big big birthday! I love you to the moon and back, and now that I know where the moon is, I really mean I would...
data.meta_description:
31K likes, 429 comments - chelseahandler on August 31, 2022: "To my brother Roy on his big big birthday! 

I love you to the moon and back, and now that I know where the moon is, I really mean I would travel that distance to spend time with you. 

Because you are so funny, so sweet, you are without guile, and because you always rub my feet like I'm your baby. 
I'm so happy you found love and that you are now someone's husband and that you get to receive all the love you have bestowed on all of us. 

You are a gentle soul, Royboy, and you have so much of Mom in you, and my love and gratitude for you grows every year. 

We all love you so much. Watching all our nieces and nephews get your sense of humor and appreciate you the way we all do makes my heart sing and reminds me that you are timeless.

Happy Birthday, Royboy! You are beloved.".
